                        <Font name="Segoe UI Semibold" size="25.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Text layoutX="27.0" layoutY="1046.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Physics is at the core of many technological advancements and plays a key role in addressing environmental challenges. From designing energy-efficient buildings to developing renewable energy sources like solar panels and wind turbines, physics helps us understand and harness the forces of nature responsibly. Concepts like energy transfer, thermodynamics, and electromagnetism are central to these innovations." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="27.0" layoutY="1163.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="In environmental monitoring, physics enables us to track weather patterns, detect pollutants, and model climate change using satellite systems and sensors. In medicine, technologies like X-rays, CT scans, and radiation therapy are rooted in physics principles. The integration of physics in modern applications not only improves quality of life but also equips us with tools to build a more sustainable and technologically advanced future." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
